title: LF Plat+ Top, jungle, and support to make a team
body:
Hello All,

Have a great ADC and I am a mid main. If you are interested in practicing 2-3 times a week, expanding your champion pool, and developing your game knowledge this is the team for you. add me in game or on discord LeftyRaydy#6619 and respond with below.

Age -
Current rank in League
Highest Rank achieved in League
Main Role
Secondary Role
top 3 champions for your primary role
Time Zone -
availability to practice each week
